



// Video desc 1
In this video I show you how to make a javaScript game (or animation! or simulation!) from scratch.

First video in short series of...maybe 3?

Tutorial 2: https://youtu.be/3QiqjfCmmag
Tutorial 3: https://youtu.be/gDcgdly1nnc

Here's the code used in this tutorial: http://codepen.io/RedHenDev/pen/WjxrdR

