// video 3
In this (third) video I show you how to use collisions between objects to have an effect on those objects, such as bouncing off one another, and drawing 'connecting lines' between objects that have collided before. Will this look cool -- or disgusting?!

The code used in this tutorial: http://codepen.io/RedHenDev/pen/XRKepG

